    LlamaStackOp -->|creates/manages| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaims]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates/manages| Ingress[Ingress Resources]
    LlamaStackOp -->|creates/manages| NetPol[NetworkPolicies]
