    LlamaStackOp -->|creates/manages| PDB[PodDisruptionBudgets]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    LlamaStackDeploy -->|inference| Ollama
    LlamaStackDeploy -->|inference| vLLM
    vLLM -->|model download| HuggingFace

